      <p>HÜLSMANN, Jörg Guido. Economic Science and Neoclassicism. Quarterly Journal of Austrian Economics, v. 2, n. 4. p. 4-6. Winter, 1999. <a href="#fnref:26" class="reversefootnote" role="doc-backlink">&#8617;</a></p>
